      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and restoration lovers! This vehicle is looking for a fresh start and is the perfect project for someone who loves to get their hands dirty. While it's currently in poor condition and needs some TLC to get back on the road, it offers a fantastic, budget-friendly opportunity to rebuild a classic to your own specifications!",
