      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Boasting a consistent service history and exceptional mechanical integrity, the car offers a refined driving experience that exceeds standard expectations for its class. We invite you to inspect this well-preserved specimen, which balances sophisticated performance with lasting value.",
      "price": 36800.0,
